OL,4,G0420FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GJohn Brady likes to stand out
OL,6,     Gfrom the crowd in Liverpool with
OL,7,     Ghis unique B&B, Elegant House.
OL,8,     GBut his eclectic style and
OL,9,     Galternative breakfast aren't to
OL,10,     Geveryone's taste.
OL,11,G0445FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GPeter and Amanda introduce their
OL,13,     Gguests to the world of glamping
OL,14,     Gat Hidden Valley Yurts in
OL,15,     GMonmouthshire. But the shared
OL,16,     Gbathroom facilities and DIY
OL,17,     Gbreakfast aren't to everyone's
OL,18,     Gtaste.
