OL,4,G0515FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GDavid and Nikki host the final
OL,6,     Gvisit at Cley Hall Hotel in
OL,7,     GSpalding, Lincolnshire. But
OL,8,     Gthere's clock-watching at
OL,9,     Gbreakfast, and some of the
OL,10,     Gguests' comments leave the hosts
OL,11,     Gfuming.
OL,12,G0540FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GIt's the final day of the
OL,14,     Gcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,15,     Gfor the last time to discover how
OL,16,     Gmuch they've been paid and
OL,17,     Gconfront their critics, before
OL,18,     Gthe winner is announced.
